---
const title = 'Momentum — Time tracking for makers';
const description =
  'Momentum helps makers track real project time in seconds, with a frictionless macOS workflow and Raycast extension.';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0b1020;
        --card: #141b34;
        --text: #edf2ff;
        --muted: #b6c0e4;
        --accent: #7c9cff;
        --line: #273362;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #151f3e 0%, var(--bg) 55%);
        color: var(--text);
      }
      .container { max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem; }
      .hero {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 3.5rem 1rem 2rem;
      }
      h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.6rem); margin: 0 0 0.8rem; }
      p { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
      .lead { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; }
      .actions { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .btn {
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.1rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      .btn.primary { background: var(--accent); color: #0b1020; }
      .btn.ghost { border-color: #36467f; color: var(--text); }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
      .card {
        background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--card), black 8%);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 1rem;
      }
      h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.05rem; }
      .section { margin-top: 2.2rem; }

      .screenshots {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .shot {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 14px;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #0f1530;
      }
      .shot .ph {
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1c2750, #0e1430);
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        color: #9cb0ff;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .shot p { margin: 0; padding: 0.8rem; }

      .waitlist { text-align: center; }
      .waitlist form {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.6rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      input[type="email"] {
        min-width: 280px;
        max-width: 420px;
        width: 100%;
        border: 1px solid #3a4b87;
        background: #0c1230;
        color: var(--text);
        padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
      }

      details {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
        background: #0f1530;
      }
      details + details { margin-top: 0.7rem; }
      summary { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; }

      .final-cta { text-align: center; }

      footer {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        color: #98a6d8;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero" id="top">
        <p style="margin:0;opacity:.9;">Momentum for macOS</p>
        <h1>Know where your project time actually goes.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Most makers don't have a time problem — they have a visibility problem. Momentum lets you log sessions in seconds,
          organize work by project, and review your week with data you can trust. No spreadsheets. No admin overhead.
          Just clear signal on what is moving your work forward.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn primary" href="#waitlist">Join waitlist</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="#how">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid section" id="how">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Capture in seconds</h2>
          <p>Start and stop sessions fast, so tracking supports flow instead of breaking it.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Organize by project</h2>
          <p>Group your time where it matters and spot what deserves more attention.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Log from Raycast</h2>
          <p>Use the built-in Raycast extension to track instantly from anywhere on macOS.</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Screenshots</h2>
        <div class="screenshots">
          <article class="shot">
            <div class="ph">Dashboard screenshot</div>
            <p>Quickly see project totals, trends, and where your focus is really going.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="shot">
            <div class="ph">Session logging screenshot</div>
            <p>Log focused work in seconds and keep momentum through your sprint blocks.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="shot">
            <div class="ph">Raycast extension screenshot</div>
            <p>Track without context switching. One shortcut, one command, done.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section card waitlist" id="waitlist">
        <h2>Get early access</h2>
        <p>
          Momentum is currently in the final polish phase. Join the waitlist to get launch updates,
          early access, and first release notes.
        </p>
        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id" method="POST">
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@domain.com" required />
          <button class="btn primary" type="submit">Join waitlist</button>
        </form>
        <p style="font-size:.9rem;margin-top:.8rem;">Tip: replace the Formspree endpoint with your own.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="faq">
        <h2>FAQ</h2>
        <details>
          <summary>Who is Momentum for?</summary>
          <p>Developers, designers, and makers doing project-based work who want clear time data with minimal friction.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Do I need to track every minute?</summary>
          <p>No. Momentum is built for practical clarity, not micromanagement. Track enough to make better decisions.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>What's the main difference vs generic trackers?</summary>
          <p>Speed and focus. Momentum is optimized for maker workflows, with a native macOS flow and Raycast support.</p>
        </details>
      </section>

      <section class="section card final-cta">
        <h2>Track less. Understand more. Ship better.</h2>
        <p>Turn weekly time logs into better prioritization and faster product progress.</p>
        <a class="btn primary" href="#waitlist">Join waitlist</a>
      </section>

      <footer>
        Built by Miguel · Momentum
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
